      _TV Show Notes_ 
      ===============----------------------------------------------------
       
       Ireland v New Zealand (Kick-off 5.15pm). John Inverdale presents 
       coverage of the Test match at Croke Park, where Declan Kidney's 
       men face the Tri Nations champions in their first match at Croke 
       Park this season. The last meeting between the two sides was in 
       June this year at Wellington's Westpac Stadium, where Ireland led
       on three occasions but ended up on the receiving end of a 21-11 
       defeat. With commentary by Eddie Butler and Phillip Matthews 

